  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/9721c870089d8378318ce199cc62fbbc.webp?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=37 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/7ef1756f686771984c193ddc84292c39.avif?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=88 /></span><br><br><strong>Join forces with your villagers</strong> to battle the malevolent Demon Herensuge and his army of hellish minions & elites, intent on wreaking havoc on your serene homeland. Use your deck-building skills to emerge victorious from the perilous depths of the Pyrenees.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/2ade7f811d4dc323bdd57515221f4088.poster.avif?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/2ade7f811d4dc323bdd57515221f4088.webm?t=1752528241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/2ade7f811d4dc323bdd57515221f4088.mp4?t=1752528241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Experiment with various characters</strong> each with distinct abilities and traits that enable a wide range of gameplay styles. Develop different strategies and optimize the use of items you collect to enhance your abilities on every adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/f59a5f9cbb3fc6e8237160e536488851.poster.avif?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/f59a5f9cbb3fc6e8237160e536488851.webm?t=1752528241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/f59a5f9cbb3fc6e8237160e536488851.mp4?t=1752528241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Upgrade your deck</strong> by unlocking over 200 powerful relics and 100+ cards that you can switch on-the-fly to maximize your deck in between enemy encounters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/4af5a5250842fc504d141981c1c8fa01.poster.avif?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/4af5a5250842fc504d141981c1c8fa01.webm?t=1752528241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/4af5a5250842fc504d141981c1c8fa01.mp4?t=1752528241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fight through distinct biomes</strong> such as dark caverns, corrupted swamps, menacing mountains, each with their own set of creatures and terrain modifiers.<br>Between expeditions, return to your village and restore buildings to <strong>unlock upgrades for your items and spells</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/45e77998fd1f624c6eea252ae106d936.poster.avif?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/45e77998fd1f624c6eea252ae106d936.webm?t=1752528241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/45e77998fd1f624c6eea252ae106d936.mp4?t=1752528241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/9721c870089d8378318ce199cc62fbbc.webp?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=37 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/8a3adc580ffd904cb1e2322c962a57c9.avif?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=88 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><i>Uncharted Setting:</i></strong> Pyrene is based on Basque mythology, a never-before seen pantheon in video games. Learn more about these untold stories, deities and creatures by playing.<br></li><li><strong><i>Strategic Decision-Making:</i></strong> Balanced between ease of play and strategy, Pyrene presents deep deck-building elements that intertwine with its dungeon-crawling gameplay to force you to think before making any move.<br></li><li><strong><i>Unique Characters:</i></strong> Play as a diverse cast of characters from your village, each one possessing unique skills, mechanics and magic. Tailor your deck to your hero to make the most of each run!<br></li><li><strong><i>Built for Replayability:</i></strong> With a wide range of objects, biomes, relics, talismans & spells, no two runs are the same and you will be able to develop ingenuous strategies to navigate the game’s story and endless modes YOUR way. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2468100/extras/9721c870089d8378318ce199cc62fbbc.webp?t=1752528241\" width=600 height=37 /></span>",
